	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "When sent ahead by Varus to Corsica, he made an agreement which was repudiated; whereupon he was delivered to the Corsi, returned by them, and then either imprisoned or banished (Val. Max. 6.3.3; Zon. 8.18; cf. Dio fr. 45; Ammian. 14.11.32)." .
